text: Richard Rösler (25 August 1881 - 1 June 1969) was a German swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1969 deaths Category:German male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Germany Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wrocław
